# Personal-data blocklist for the pre-commit hook.
#
# Copy this file to ".githooks/blocklist" (gitignored) and add one
# substring per line. Matching is case-insensitive and literal (no regex).
# Empty lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# Suggested categories (fill in your actual values in the local copy,
# never here):
#
#   # Real names & nicknames (Cyrillic + Latin)
#   YourFirstName
#   YourLastName
#   YourPartner
#
#   # Real channel ids (VK numeric, Telegram numeric, etc.)
#   123456789
#
#   # Email
#   you@example.com
#
#   # Production hosts / IPs
#   prod.example.com
#   203.0.113.42
#
#   # Secret tokens / API keys (also catch leaked tokens before push)
#   AQVN...
